            <!--About US-->
            <div id="Aboutus" class="page-section">
                <div class="container">
                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="col-md-12">
                            <div class="section-heading">
                                <h4>About Us</h4>
                                <div class="line-dec"></div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="col-md-6">
                            <div class="item b1">
                                <div class="thumb">
                                    <div class="text-content">
                                        <p>
                                            Under the theme of Changing Melbourne,
                                            the team Melbourne Wizards focus is on improving women safety in Melbourne city centre.
                                            Green Umbrella is such a product would be able to display safety index scores of areas in and around Melbourne CBD
                                            the website can be viewed both on a personal computer and a mobile device.
                                            It will be able to show safety index score based on user preference.
                                            The underlying support of achieving the above function is a list of datasets from multiple open data platforms.
                                        </p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-md-6 team-logo"></div>
                    </div>
                </div>
